{"tid":939824,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"三月 - 伊朗 土耳其 希臘 埃及","createTime":"2018-12-13T12:06:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T22:27:02.000Z","uid":76012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1ef2ac8253ffd44fc77711a4117f5434894d25a2","tid":939824,"uid":76012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T12:06:24.000Z","msg":"詳細行程重plan緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但大約行程就如下:<br />\n伊朗(07-17/3):<br />\n設拉子<br />\n伊斯法罕<br />\n德黑蘭<br />\n<br />\n土耳其(17-27/3):<br />\n伊斯坦堡<br />\n棉花堡<br />\n圖茲湖<br />\n內夫謝希爾<br />\n<br />\n希臘(27-31/3):<br />\n雅典<br />\n聖托里尼<br />\n<br />\n埃及(31/3-04/4):<br />\n開羅<br />\n<br />\n咁多位巴絲有冇去過邊到，可以比啲意見交流下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eead371c69fd57c3c2d9d2ec75676bc68c9f2e51","tid":939824,"uid":138785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T14:25:19.000Z","msg":"棉花堡轉卡帕都奇亞會好啲"},{"pid":"692ad725d54936c2b351da108e509f5c1b59cf78","tid":939824,"uid":36461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T03:01:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>棉花堡轉卡帕都奇亞會好啲</blockquote><br />\n樓主個plan咪有Cappadocia"},{"pid":"a26e2db1a32105b32a33b6e7261a2661427dd691","tid":939824,"uid":138785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"692ad725d54936c2b351da108e509f5c1b59cf78","tid":939824,"uid":36461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T03:01:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>棉花堡轉卡帕都奇亞會好啲</blockquote><br />\n樓主個plan咪有Cappadocia"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T05:05:10.000Z","msg":"我去哂兩道<br />\n棉堡污染得勁，黃同埋冇水，仲有多人<br />\n我已經打算他朝一日棉堡修復嘅時候再去多次turk (導遊話起碼要等廿幾三十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n卡城真係好值得去，啲地形真係一生難忘，同埋多景點，例如red valley, 洞穴教堂，洞穴酒店應該唔貴，好值得一試"},{"pid":"76df7b088e2b629f50b701a9e81c034c22fd119c","tid":939824,"uid":138785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T05:26:12.000Z","msg":"oh我唔知內夫謝希爾係卡城<br />\nsor<img src=\"/as